         throws com.qualitestgroup.kdt.framework.exceptions.KDTParseException
        Creates a Test Step. If the keyword is not found in the given application, the Universal class is searched.
        Parameters:
        keyword - The keyword to run.
        app - The application to find the keyword in.
        ID - The test case ID.

        com.qualitestgroup.kdt.framework.exceptions.KDTParseException - If keyword parsing fails.

      • run

        public boolean run()
            throws com.qualitestgroup.kdt.framework.exceptions.KDTException

        Throws:
        com.qualitestgroup.kdt.framework.exceptions.KDTException - If the keyword fails to execute and the keyword's stopTestOnFail attribute is set to true.
